<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p><rs type="material">White marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">block</rs> (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.68</measure> x <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.84</measure> x <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.28</measure>); there are three holes in the top for an attachment. Part of a composite monument.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p>inscribed on one face which is damaged along all edges. The text began on an upper block, and continued on a lower one or on one adjacent to the right.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>late Republican: ll. 1, 2, av. <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.028</measure>; ll. 3, 4, av. <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.024</measure> ; ll. 5-17, av. <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.022</measure>; ll. 18-20, av. <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.018</measure>; Α at the end of 1. 4 written small.</p>
</div>
